7.content:
studies purchase TS2PathFull
unlock dilation
studies nowait purchase TSFull
if tp <= 10 {
  start dilation
  pause 0.1s
  eternity

9.name: Glyph
9.content:
infinity
eternity nowait respec

if total tt < 417 {
  studies purchase TSTDActive
  studies purchase 181
  wait total tt > 417
  eternity respec
}

if ep < 1e900 {
  auto infinity off
  studies purchase TS2PathFull
  wait ep >= 1e900
  eternity respec
}

studies purchase TS2PathFull

// Unlock dilation - Gives 10 TP
wait tt >= 5100
unlock dilation
eternity respec
studies purchase TSFirstDil
start dilation
wait ip >= 2e308
eternity respec
studies load name Main


studies purchase TSFull

auto eternity off


wait pending glyph level > 16260
reality
